{"tid":2497582,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺歐超聯呢單嘢成功瓦解咗波台狗集團？","createTime":"2021-04-20T15:24:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T16:36:04.000Z","uid":73381,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"35d0bc3edf292a12130912ef8044e96dcb655eff","tid":2497582,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T15:24:52.000Z","msg":"眾所周知 波台狗係由重光團隊+PR集團+五毛狗組成<br />\n<br />\n美國佬搞嘅歐超聯突登喺呢個時候公佈 似係祖。拜登(Mr. President Joe Burden)落咗柯打 要轉移班波台狗事線 令到班撚樣全部集中討論歐超聯<br />\n<br />\nPR同五毛無瑕再搞分化 重光狗亦都唔得閒再狙擊攬炒巴<br />\n<br />\n冇咗呢班撚樣阻住哂 收到風習近平平大哥嬲到咸咗 如今我哋時事台手足需要做嘅就係維持歐超聯嘅熱度 實行愈亂愈好 令到波台班能樣繼續疲於奔命<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61346d0eac240b73843cf1caaf9b2254ac764f22","tid":2497582,"uid":199081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T15:25:56.000Z","msg":"少咗人攻擊龍門"},{"pid":"6f28bf1ae41ceefe07d4a5869d9075751943eeda","tid":2497582,"uid":372210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T15:26:02.000Z","msg":"原來捉緊盤咁大嘅棋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"074930102153d302f96c3e025d528704e94c13e2","tid":2497582,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"61346d0eac240b73843cf1caaf9b2254ac764f22","tid":2497582,"uid":199081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T15:25:56.000Z","msg":"少咗人攻擊龍門"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T15:27:12.000Z","msg":"拜登大總統(登仔)今次真係幫條哥幫到盡一盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f74a940a7447e7d3a2aa76d03471bb506adda36f","tid":2497582,"uid":73381,"like":0,"d